This paper discusses a novel approach to unsupervised learning within a framework that integrates various AI functions such as language parsing, pattern recognition, and reasoning. Therefore, it is likely to be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), information theory (cs.IT), and computer vision (cs.CV).
